title: Farseer - William King.epub
description:
The eldar race once sailed the length of the galaxy in their craftworlds, seeking knowledge and enlightenment in the darkest corners and unwittingly unleashing a power that threatened to destroy them. Now a dying race, the eldar rely on the farseers to see the futures. By manipulating events, the eldar can bring peace, for a time. But they must find a agent--one very special human--and convince him to do their bidding.
Genre: Sci-fi
